 ниже +8 С для водо-дисперсионных красок)).</p><p>В случае ненадлежащего выполнения обращения в отношении ТСЖ будут применены меры административного воздействия.</p><p>Обращение остается на контроле администрации района до 04.05.2021г.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Невского района","performer":null,"response_performers":[],"files":[{"id":18036792,"url":"/storage/2/0eaaa037-0cef-4caa-95f6-fd1e0d67931d.pdf","original_name":"Untitled.FR12.pdf"}],"photos":[],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-05-04"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13070915","payload":{"id":13070915,"dt":"2021-02-11T12:42:18.397207","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13064562","payload":{"id":13064562,"dt":"2021-02-10T22:11:45.674658","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3543043","payload":{"id":3543043,"dt":"2021-02-10T22:11:45.556627","status_name":"Промежуточный ответ","body":[{"text":"надписи на стене","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/5237eff4-c98b-46aa-bf41-639c37f59840.jpg","original_name":"IMG-20210210-WA0253.jpg","id":4015493,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/24/a7/24a7568402a85af75e1031f3fdfea237.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/5237eff4-c98b-46aa-bf41-639c37f59840.jpg","size":"960x1280"},{"url":"/storage/1/fd48beb0-d659-4acb-9be0-ad2d203e579a.jpg","original_name":"IMG-20210210-WA0254.jpg","id":4015494,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/af/39/af39cc53499034297a8092a7d82bf774.jpg","original_url":"/storag